        %p I've included my demo reel here to show my background. I decided to leave the film industry in 2013 because of the state of the industry. Due to lower box office numbers and DVD sales, as well as tax incentives in foreign countries, most of the studios in the U.S. were closing.
      %script{:src => "https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"}
